(25, 'updated-eway-payment-gateway-rin-2022-12-20', 'update', 'en_US', 'WooCommerce Eway Gateway has been automatically updated', 'Your store is now running the latest secure version of WooCommerce Eway Gateway. We worked with the WordPress Plugins team to deploy a software update to stores running WooCommerce Eway Gateway (versions 3.1.0 to 3.5.0) in response to a security vulnerability that was discovered.', '{}', 'pending', 'woocommerce.com', '2024-05-28 18:12:10', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info'),
